  "prompt": "How is the academics in Hindu Rao Medical College?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, Hindu Rao Medical College is not typically listed among the top medical colleges in India. However, it is affiliated with the prestigious Hindu Rao Hospital, which is one of the largest hospitals run by the Municipal Corporation of Delhi. \n\nThe college offers undergraduate and postgraduate medical courses, and students benefit from the clinical exposure provided by the hospital. The faculty is experienced, and the institution focuses on providing practical training alongside theoretical knowledge.\n\nThe academic environment at Hindu Rao Medical College can be described as rigorous, with an emphasis on hands-on clinical experience. Students often appreciate the real-world exposure they get due to the hospital's diverse patient base. However, as with many medical colleges, the quality of education can vary depending on factors such as infrastructure, faculty, and available resources.\n\nProspective students should consider these aspects and, if possible, seek feedback from current students or alumni to get a comprehensive understanding of the academic atmosphere at Hindu Rao Medical College.",
